:<div class="mw-parser-output"><h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Table_of_villagers">Table of villagers</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=List_of_villagers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Table of villagers">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>Character names in <i>italics</i> denote Japanese-exclusive villagers whose names have not been localized in other regions.
